be airing our dirty laundry?

298
00:13:30,850 --> 00:13:31,730
But

299
00:13:32,190 --> 00:13:33,540
I don't see this

300
00:13:34,300 --> 00:13:36,100
as a family matter.

301
00:13:36,130 --> 00:13:37,750
How do you not see that?

302
00:13:38,210 --> 00:13:40,210
If this were our family's business,

303
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:42,150
then why is the tap

304
00:13:42,170 --> 00:13:43,170
locked?

305
00:13:44,060 --> 00:13:46,060
If this were our family's business,

306
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:47,260
why is the cutting board

307
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:48,780
cleared off so clean,

308
00:13:48,780 --> 00:13:50,540
and I can't even light the stove?

309
00:13:50,540 --> 00:13:51,940
If this were our family's business,

310
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:53,760
why are all these jars put away?

311
00:13:54,490 --> 00:13:56,620
You're guarding against me like this?

312
00:13:57,530 --> 00:13:59,360
So, how come I don't feel like

313
00:13:59,390 --> 00:14:00,870
we are family?

314
00:14:03,260 --> 00:14:04,190
You locked them?

315
00:14:05,230 --> 00:14:05,610
Hey.

316
00:14:05,610 --> 00:14:07,450
Why are you guarding
against Sister-in-law?

317
00:14:07,450 --> 00:14:09,380
