321
00:14:14,020 --> 00:14:15,260
running like it's the Huangpu River.

322
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:16,570
Once it's on, she never turns it off.

323
00:14:16,570 --> 00:14:18,180
She doesn't care about the waste at all.

324
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:19,660
The two kids of the traveling merchant

325
00:14:19,660 --> 00:14:20,710
