520
00:22:46,050 --> 00:22:46,970
Hello.

521
00:22:47,970 --> 00:22:48,580
Ms. Ding.

522
00:22:48,630 --> 00:22:49,350
Please have a seat.

523
00:22:49,350 --> 00:22:50,540
I have a court session this afternoon.

524
00:22:50,540 --> 00:22:51,770
Lawyer Wu is not here?

525
00:22:52,050 --> 00:22:53,650
He went back to his hometown.

526
00:22:53,860 --> 00:22:54,580
About your matter,

527
00:22:54,580 --> 00:22:55,790
he asked for you.

528
00:22:55,970 --> 00:22:57,340
During the heavy rains two years ago,

529
00:22:57,340 --> 00:22:59,420
several crates of court registry records
were damaged by flooding,

530
00:22:59,420 --> 00:23:01,210
including the 21st year
of the Republic of China's

531
00:23:01,210 --> 00:23:02,410
property registers.

532
00:23:02,730 --> 00:23:03,380
Then,

533
00:23:03,860 --> 00:23:05,050
