534
00:23:05,050 --> 00:23:06,690
Does that mean there's no way to prove

535
00:23:06,690 --> 00:23:08,350
that this house belongs to us?

536
00:23:08,690 --> 00:23:09,570
Unless

537
00:23:09,620 --> 00:23:12,350
you can find the proof of purchase
from that year.

538
00:23:13,010 --> 00:23:14,010
The proof is probably

539
00:23:14,010 --> 00:23:16,340
at my husband's house in the countryside.

540
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:18,530
But now it's occupied by the Japanese.

541
00:23:18,530 --> 00:23:20,140
We can't get it back.

542
00:23:20,820 --> 00:23:22,180
Ms. Ding, please don't worry.

543
00:23:22,180 --> 00:23:23,420
After Lawyer Wu finishes
his family matters,

544
00:23:23,420 --> 00:23:24,680
