559
00:23:54,380 --> 00:23:55,310
It keeps you warm

560
00:23:55,340 --> 00:23:56,940
and replenishes your blood.

561
00:23:58,770 --> 00:23:59,630
Short of money?

562
00:24:00,380 --> 00:24:01,840
You can get paid for blood.

563
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:02,940
Hey.

564
00:24:13,310 --> 00:24:15,030
