565
00:24:15,060 --> 00:24:16,170
First time here?

566
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,380
Scared already?

567
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:18,400
It's quick money.

568
00:24:18,860 --> 00:24:20,180
Quick money?

569
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:20,860
Look,

570
00:24:20,900 --> 00:24:21,250
