572
00:24:22,450 --> 00:24:24,400
He makes money really fast.

573
00:24:24,470 --> 00:24:26,560
He takes a 30% cut of every deal.

574
00:24:26,580 --> 00:24:27,510
That's robbery!

575
00:24:28,340 --> 00:24:29,380
That's how it works here.

576
00:24:29,380 --> 00:24:30,940
What, like we can just skip it?

577
00:24:30,940 --> 00:24:31,530
No.

578
00:24:31,820 --> 00:24:33,880
After that, go have some fun at Ciros.

579
00:24:34,290 --> 00:24:34,900
The little money I have

580
00:24:34,900 --> 00:24:36,690
is kept for supporting my family.

581
00:24:36,690 --> 00:24:37,180
Brother,

582
00:24:37,180 --> 00:24:38,660
