587
00:24:43,940 --> 00:24:45,730
and each time it was 400 milliliters.

588
00:24:45,730 --> 00:24:46,620
As a result, the last time,

589
00:24:46,620 --> 00:24:47,660
the younger sister

590
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:50,290
collapsed and died right after donating.

591
00:24:50,290 --> 00:24:51,050
Madam,

592
00:24:51,340 --> 00:24:52,710
raising a child costs a lot of money,
doesn't it?

593
00:24:52,710 --> 00:24:54,170
You can get paid for blood.

594
00:24:57,490 --> 00:24:58,250
Are you short of money?

595
00:24:58,250 --> 00:24:59,060
How much?

596
00:24:59,140 --> 00:24:59,900
8 silver dollars.

597
00:24:59,900 --> 00:25:00,660
8 silver dollars!

598
00:25:00,660 --> 00:25:01,660
Then I'll donate.

599
00:25:01,730 --> 00:25:03,300
Go line up at the back.

600
00:25:04,570 --> 00:25:05,570
[Liangxin Blood Donation Center]

601
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,810
Sister-in-law, time to eat.

602
00:25:29,210 --> 00:25:30,340
Need any help?

603
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:31,210
No.

604
00:25:31,210 --> 00:25:32,340
I'm all done.

605
00:25:32,860 --> 00:25:33,860
Where is the baby?

606
00:25:34,050 --> 00:25:34,910
He's sleeping.

607
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:36,510
Sister-in-law.

608
00:25:36,660 --> 00:25:37,860
I know you Wuxi people

609
00:25:37,860 --> 00:25:39,180
love Wuxi-style spare ribs

610
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:40,530
and three Whites of Taihu Lake.

611
00:25:40,530 --> 00:25:42,010
Unfortunately, recently,

612
00:25:42,010 --> 00:25:43,100
the season is wrong,

613
00:25:43,100 --> 00:25:44,250
things are in chaos,

614
00:25:44,250 --> 00:25:45,580
and supplies are scarce.

615
00:25:45,580 --> 00:25:46,530
So I went to see Granny Cao

616
00:25:46,530 --> 00:25:47,940
early this morning

617
00:25:48,050 --> 00:25:49,290
and asked her to pick

618
00:25:49,290 --> 00:25:50,900
the freshest perch she could find.

619
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:52,050
Why don't you make do

620
00:25:52,050 --> 00:25:53,650
and try our Songjiang perch?

621
00:25:53,690 --> 00:25:55,340
It's a local specialty, too.

622
00:25:55,820 --> 00:25:57,100
Thank you, Shuyuan.

623
00:25:57,100 --> 00:25:57,820
Sorry for the trouble.

624
00:25:57,820 --> 00:25:58,490
No problem.

625
00:25:59,490 --> 00:26:00,410
Where is Yunqi?

626
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:01,490
He hasn't come back yet.

627
00:26:01,490 --> 00:26:02,730
Shall we wait for him?

628
00:26:03,180 --> 00:26:03,840
Him?

629
00:26:03,860 --> 00:26:05,140
Who knows where he's run off to,

630
00:26:05,140 --> 00:26:06,490
messing around.

631
00:26:06,690 --> 00:26:07,330
It's fine.

632
00:26:07,490 --> 00:26:08,730
He likes eating leftovers anyway.

633
00:26:08,730 --> 00:26:10,380
Let's eat first. Don't worry about him.

634
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:10,770
Here.

635
00:26:10,860 --> 00:26:11,580
Thank you.

636
00:26:11,860 --> 00:26:16,580
♪ Other folks have nice arched brows... ♪

637
00:26:16,770 --> 00:26:19,180
♪ Mine just... ♪

638
00:26:19,180 --> 00:26:20,010
You're back.

639
00:26:20,210 --> 00:26:21,140
Sister-in-law.

640
00:26:22,390 --> 00:26:23,820
Nothing but the good stuff.

641
00:26:23,820 --> 00:26:24,420
Look,

642
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:25,690
they are all Sister-in-law's favorites.

643
00:26:25,690 --> 00:26:27,690
I'm helping her build her strength.

644
00:26:29,190 --> 00:26:30,180
I just remembered

645
00:26:30,180 --> 00:26:31,180
did you

646
00:26:31,180 --> 00:26:32,140
go out

647
00:26:32,140 --> 00:26:33,420
to take care of something today?

648
00:26:33,420 --> 00:26:34,450
How did it go?

649
00:26:34,450 --> 00:26:35,690
Right, Sister-in-law.

650
00:26:35,690 --> 00:26:37,140
Did things go smoothly?

651
00:26:37,940 --> 00:26:39,010
Quite smoothly.

652
00:26:41,530 --> 00:26:42,580
The lawyer

653
00:26:42,580 --> 00:26:45,050
has already found the records
at the Court Registry.

654
00:26:45,050 --> 00:26:46,940
The buyer, the seller,

655
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:48,420
the size of the house,

656
00:26:48,420 --> 00:26:49,490
the address,

657
00:26:49,490 --> 00:26:50,290
the guarantors...

658
00:26:50,290 --> 00:26:52,050
even the tax deed's been found.

659
00:26:52,620 --> 00:26:53,840
This afternoon,

660
00:26:53,970 --> 00:26:55,010
I've already filed

661
00:26:55,010 --> 00:26:56,380
for a replacement deed.

662
00:26:56,450 --> 00:26:57,100
Heaven rewards

663
00:26:57,100 --> 00:26:58,960
the faithful.

664
00:26:59,250 --> 00:27:00,340
That's great.

665
00:27:01,490 --> 00:27:02,900
It's just the court's

666
00:27:02,900 --> 00:27:03,420
a bit short-handed

667
00:27:03,420 --> 00:27:04,250
right now,

668
00:27:04,250 --> 00:27:05,050
so...

669
00:27:05,820 --> 00:27:07,050
it might take a few more months

670
00:27:07,050 --> 00:27:07,990
to get it done.

671
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:09,580
A few more months?

672
00:27:15,290 --> 00:27:16,170
Zhang Yunqi.

673
00:27:16,490 --> 00:27:18,340
You went for a walk outside.

674
00:27:18,490 --> 00:27:19,730
Did you attract some dirty spirits?

675
00:27:19,730 --> 00:27:21,130
Why are you acting crazy?

676
00:27:23,620 --> 00:27:25,290
Sorry, Sister-in-law.

677
00:27:29,730 --> 00:27:31,690
Regardless of where you are from,

678
00:27:31,970 --> 00:27:33,820
everyone, old or young,

679
00:27:33,820 --> 00:27:36,180
has a duty to defend the land.

680
00:27:36,210 --> 00:27:37,620
Who said this?

681
00:27:38,180 --> 00:27:40,310
It's Generalissimo Chiang's slogan.

682
00:27:40,620 --> 00:27:42,350
Our family—

683
00:27:43,450 --> 00:27:45,000
Fisherman, woodcutter,
farmer, and scholar—

684
00:27:45,000 --> 00:27:47,210
We're a family
of scholars and etiquette.

685
00:27:47,210 --> 00:27:50,100
Frugality is our tradition,

686
00:27:50,900 --> 00:27:52,830
passed down through generations.

687
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:55,050
The soldiers at the front are fighting,

688
00:27:55,050 --> 00:27:56,650
barely getting by on scraps.

689
00:27:56,690 --> 00:27:58,550
With a table full of fish and meat,

690
00:27:59,580 --> 00:28:00,970
as a Chinese,

691
00:28:01,420 --> 00:28:02,420
I

692
00:28:02,900 --> 00:28:04,620
can't live with it.

693
00:28:06,010 --> 00:28:07,690
So,

694
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:09,590
no more fish from now on.

695
00:28:09,820 --> 00:28:11,100
I, Zhang Yunqi,

696
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:12,860
you, Li Shuyuan,

697
00:28:14,050 --> 00:28:14,530
and

698
00:28:14,530 --> 00:28:15,180
you too—

699
00:28:15,180 --> 00:28:16,010
Sister-in-law...

700
00:28:16,010 --> 00:28:18,660
even the little one upstairs.

701
00:28:20,010 --> 00:28:20,860
We must

702
00:28:20,970 --> 00:28:22,250
lead by example,

703
00:28:22,450 --> 00:28:25,050
starting with what we eat.

704
00:28:25,080 --> 00:28:26,660
Are you out of your mind?

705
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,140
Didn't you tell me

706
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:29,420
that Sister-in-law hasn't finished
her confinement month yet

707
00:28:29,420 --> 00:28:30,820
and needs good nourishment?

708
00:28:30,820 --> 00:28:31,480
Besides,

709
00:28:31,530 --> 00:28:33,140
the baby upstairs

710
00:28:33,140 --> 00:28:33,820
is still nursing.

711
00:28:33,820 --> 00:28:35,490
How is he supposed
to watch what he eats?

712
00:28:35,490 --> 00:28:37,420
You mind your own mouth.

713
00:28:38,530 --> 00:28:40,660
I don't have to mind my own mouth today.

714
00:28:40,660 --> 00:28:42,180
I have my reasons.

715
00:28:45,940 --> 00:28:46,910
Sister-in-law.

716
00:28:47,690 --> 00:28:48,580
I...

717
00:28:48,820 --> 00:28:51,180
need to ask you something serious.

718
00:28:51,780 --> 00:28:53,590
For your matters today,

719
00:28:53,690 --> 00:28:56,010
did you go to Ha Tong Law Office

720
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:57,690
and have Lawyer Wu

721
00:28:57,690 --> 00:28:59,050
handle it personally?

722
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:02,690
What else?

723
00:29:02,940 --> 00:29:03,490
Well...

724
00:29:04,420 --> 00:29:05,860
That's not the point.

725
00:29:05,860 --> 00:29:08,050
I know exactly how things are.

726
00:29:08,430 --> 00:29:09,970
Lawyer Wu's father-in-law

727
00:29:10,010 --> 00:29:11,050
is seriously ill.

728
00:29:11,050 --> 00:29:12,910
He hadn't even been at the office.

729
00:29:13,250 --> 00:29:15,860
I happened to pass
by the Ha Tong Law Office,

730
00:29:15,860 --> 00:29:18,180
and my friend told me about it.

731
00:29:19,940 --> 00:29:21,100
Could it be

732
00:29:21,130 --> 00:29:23,930
that someone impersonated Lawyer Wu

733
00:29:24,050 --> 00:29:25,650
and tricked Sister-in-law?

734
00:29:25,770 --> 00:29:26,580
Nonsense.

735
00:29:26,860 --> 00:29:28,740
Why would anyone impersonate Lawyer Wu?

736
00:29:28,740 --> 00:29:30,050
What I'm worried about is

737
00:29:30,050 --> 00:29:31,530
that after all her efforts,

738
00:29:31,530 --> 00:29:32,050
she

739
00:29:32,290 --> 00:29:34,340
might not have found the record.

740
00:29:34,660 --> 00:29:35,860
Zhang Yunqi,

741
00:29:36,210 --> 00:29:37,580
you followed me?

742
00:29:38,490 --> 00:29:39,420
Sister-in-law,

743
00:29:39,730 --> 00:29:41,140
you can't put it that way.

744
00:29:41,250 --> 00:29:42,660
How could I follow you?

745
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:43,730
I just wanted

746
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:45,210
to ask around a bit

747
00:29:45,210 --> 00:29:46,100
on how to settle

748
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:47,420
the land deed issue.

749
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:50,820
A professional

750
00:29:50,940 --> 00:29:51,880
told me

751
00:29:52,140 --> 00:29:52,770
that the legal spirit

752
00:29:52,770 --> 00:29:54,730
of the French Concession

753
00:29:54,730 --> 00:29:56,210
boils down to one thing:

754
00:29:57,050 --> 00:29:58,920
maintaining the status quo.

755
00:29:59,100 --> 00:30:00,380
See? They made it very clear.

756
00:30:00,380 --> 00:30:01,580
I have it all written down.

757
00:30:01,580 --> 00:30:04,940
If the neighbors can prove

758
00:30:04,970 --> 00:30:08,180
that the landlord
has lived here for a long time,

759
00:30:08,290 --> 00:30:10,620
they can apply for a land deed.

760
00:30:11,830 --> 00:30:12,460
Look.

761
00:30:12,730 --> 00:30:13,900
They made it very clear.

762
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:15,660
And they even have precedent cases.

763
00:30:15,660 --> 00:30:16,170
Look,

764
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,800
Assistant Manager Mu

765
00:30:17,820 --> 00:30:18,660
from the foreign firm

766
00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:20,820
was in pretty much the same situation.

767
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:21,970
He couldn't find his land deed.

768
00:30:21,970 --> 00:30:22,580
What did he do?

769
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:23,350
He

770
00:30:23,620 --> 00:30:25,250
found his neighbors

771
00:30:25,250 --> 00:30:25,850
to prove

772
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:27,900
that he had lived there for a long time

773
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:29,430
and the place was ruled his.

774
00:30:30,010 --> 00:30:32,290
Then there's your fellow Ningbo native—

775
00:30:32,450 --> 00:30:35,580
-No. 72 Bugao Lane.
-Yes, No. 72.

776
00:30:35,660 --> 00:30:36,620
Miss Shen?

777
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:38,010
Miss Shen.

778
00:30:38,380 --> 00:30:39,900
Her case is even stranger.

779
00:30:40,010 --> 00:30:42,670
She's never even seen
the land deed to her place.

780
00:30:42,820 --> 00:30:43,420
What did she do?

781
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:45,690
She also found her neighbors to prove

782
00:30:45,690 --> 00:30:46,900
that she had lived

783
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:48,620
in that house since childhood.

784
00:30:48,620 --> 00:30:49,250
And look

785
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:50,800
at her now.

786
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:51,730
She's living in that grand house,

787
00:30:51,730 --> 00:30:53,990
doing better than anyone could imagine.

788
00:31:02,100 --> 00:31:03,470
No wonder.

789
00:31:04,420 --> 00:31:04,900
You

790
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:06,010
wouldn't let me touch the soup

791
00:31:06,010 --> 00:31:07,620
or the fish.

792
00:31:07,970 --> 00:31:09,730
And all that talk about，
"Regardless of where you are from,

793
00:31:09,730 --> 00:31:10,860
everyone, old or young—"

794
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:12,860
Making all that long-winded talk.

795
00:31:12,860 --> 00:31:13,580
So,

796
00:31:14,180 --> 00:31:15,530
this is what you're really after.

797
00:31:15,530 --> 00:31:16,100
No.

798
00:31:16,170 --> 00:31:17,690
Ever since we talked about

799
00:31:17,690 --> 00:31:19,050
this house last time,

800
00:31:19,050 --> 00:31:20,310
you two

801
00:31:20,530 --> 00:31:22,050
have been so attentive,

802
00:31:22,180 --> 00:31:23,860
playing the perfect hosts.

803
00:31:23,970 --> 00:31:26,820
You must be exhausted

804
00:31:27,530 --> 00:31:29,250
from all that acting.

805
00:31:29,730 --> 00:31:30,660
Zhang Yunqi.

806
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:33,860
I'm your sister-in-law. Zhang Yunqi!

807
00:31:34,820 --> 00:31:37,140
How could you do this?

808
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:39,340
So you're tearing things apart now?

809
00:31:39,340 --> 00:31:41,290
Tossing aside every bit

810
00:31:41,290 --> 00:31:43,150
of family affection and dignity?

811
00:31:44,140 --> 00:31:45,940
I know you're my sister-in-law.

812
00:31:46,340 --> 00:31:48,140
I never meant to fall out with you.

813
00:31:48,140 --> 00:31:48,970
But...

814
00:31:49,010 --> 00:31:49,660
that's...

815
00:31:49,660 --> 00:31:51,490
that's not how you

816
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:53,970
hold on to family or dignity.

817
00:31:54,420 --> 00:31:56,100
With truth on your side,
you can go anywhere.

818
00:31:56,100 --> 00:31:57,770
Without it, you can't take a single step.

819
00:31:57,770 --> 00:31:58,770
I've got the law

820
00:31:59,380 --> 00:32:00,450
on my side.

821
00:32:00,690 --> 00:32:02,900
I think Yunqi

822
00:32:03,010 --> 00:32:04,140
was right.

823
00:32:04,380 --> 00:32:05,900
If we use this method,

824
00:32:06,490 --> 00:32:07,890
it'll be perfectly clear

825
00:32:08,210 --> 00:32:09,770
who the real landlord is.

826
00:32:25,210 --> 00:32:27,210
Landlord or not,

827
00:32:27,420 --> 00:32:28,210
so I can't even

828
00:32:28,210 --> 00:32:29,860
take a bite of this fish today?

829
00:32:29,860 --> 00:32:30,920
What are you doing?

830
00:32:31,490 --> 00:32:32,420
Sister-in-law.

831
00:32:32,620 --> 00:32:34,210
You are right about that.

832
00:32:34,770 --> 00:32:35,820
You

833
00:32:35,820 --> 00:32:37,750
won't be touching this fish today.

834
00:32:37,900 --> 00:32:38,690
Yunqi,

835
00:32:39,010 --> 00:32:40,450
let's eat this fish together.

836
00:32:40,450 --> 00:32:41,050
If we can't finish it,

837
00:32:41,050 --> 00:32:42,140
I'll feed it to the dog tonight.

838
00:32:42,140 --> 00:32:43,380
Watch your mouth.

839
00:32:43,450 --> 00:32:44,290
She can skip the fish,

840
00:32:44,290 --> 00:32:45,970
but you shouldn't give Sister-in-law
such an attitude!

841
00:32:45,970 --> 00:32:47,290
Who wants to eat fish?

842
00:32:48,580 --> 00:32:50,110
Which dog wants to eat fish?

843
00:32:50,210 --> 00:32:51,420
Why are you back?

844
00:32:51,580 --> 00:32:52,430
I'm back.

845
00:32:52,450 --> 00:32:54,420
Look who else is back.

846
00:32:56,690 --> 00:32:58,490
No. 8 Juren Lane.

847
00:32:58,860 --> 00:32:59,900
I'm back.

848
00:33:00,010 --> 00:33:00,820
Master.

849
00:33:03,010 --> 00:33:03,660
Father.

850
00:33:04,110 --> 00:33:04,450
Father.

851
00:33:04,450 --> 00:33:05,490
Uncle!

852
00:33:06,180 --> 00:33:08,530
-Uncle, you're back.
-What is this?

853
00:33:08,530 --> 00:33:09,860
What is it?

854
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:10,580
Fish.

855
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:15,170
Yujiao.

856
00:33:15,290 --> 00:33:15,880
Father.

857
00:33:15,940 --> 00:33:17,620
Father, you're back.

858
00:33:18,580 --> 00:33:20,310
You've been through a lot.

859
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:22,280
Father, where have you been?

860
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:23,820
Why are you just coming back?

861
00:33:23,820 --> 00:33:24,440
Don't cry.

862
00:33:24,580 --> 00:33:25,380
Don't cry, child.

863
00:33:25,380 --> 00:33:25,840
Father.

864
00:33:25,860 --> 00:33:27,380
I'm fine.

865
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,360
It's good you're back.

866
00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:29,900
It's good you're back.

867
00:33:29,900 --> 00:33:30,140
Alright.

868
00:33:30,140 --> 00:33:31,340
Master. Master. Master.

869
00:33:31,340 --> 00:33:32,070
You're back.

870
00:33:32,370 --> 00:33:33,420
Take a seat.

871
00:33:34,010 --> 00:33:34,770
Okay.

872
00:33:37,290 --> 00:33:38,200
Home…

873
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:40,250
I'm home.

874
00:33:40,330 --> 00:33:41,940
We're home.

875
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:44,350
Wanfu and I have been looking for you.

876
00:33:44,450 --> 00:33:44,940
Father.

877
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:46,010
Where's Mrs. Liu?

878
00:33:46,010 --> 00:33:47,870
Why didn't she come back with you?

879
00:33:48,010 --> 00:33:48,660
Madam.

880
00:33:49,050 --> 00:33:50,660
When Master entered the concession,

881
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:52,390
he got separated from Mrs. Liu.

882
00:33:52,490 --> 00:33:54,990
And he was quite shaken.

883
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:56,060
But

884
00:33:56,340 --> 00:33:58,100
he was lucky

885
00:33:58,250 --> 00:34:00,250
and met a kind-hearted doctor

886
00:34:00,290 --> 00:34:02,900
who sent him to the hospital
for treatment.

887
00:34:02,940 --> 00:34:03,620
He

888
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:05,580
had just recovered
and was on his way back.

889
00:34:05,580 --> 00:34:06,580
What a coincidence.

890
00:34:06,580 --> 00:34:08,110
I went to the hospital
to deliver steamed buns,

891
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:09,860
and I ran into him at the gate.

892
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:11,739
So I brought him back.

893
00:34:11,739 --> 00:34:13,260
That's right.

894
00:34:14,170 --> 00:34:15,030
Just now,

895
00:34:15,130 --> 00:34:17,130
I was telling Master
on the way here.

896
00:34:18,050 --> 00:34:20,469
He must be blessed

897
00:34:20,610 --> 00:34:21,880
with great fortune.

898
00:34:22,170 --> 00:34:24,040
After such an ordeal,

899
00:34:24,090 --> 00:34:25,420
not only is he unharmed,

900
00:34:25,650 --> 00:34:27,870
but the money

901
00:34:28,260 --> 00:34:29,190
and the land deed

902
00:34:29,300 --> 00:34:30,420
are back as well,

903
00:34:30,449 --> 00:34:32,330
perfectly intact.

904
00:34:34,489 --> 00:34:35,380
Right, Master?

905
00:34:36,219 --> 00:34:37,820
That's right.

906
00:34:39,780 --> 00:34:40,940
Uncle, as I said,

907
00:34:40,940 --> 00:34:42,780
you are so kind.

908
00:34:42,810 --> 00:34:44,159
There must be

909
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:45,530
Guanyin Bodhisattva

910
00:34:45,530 --> 00:34:47,449
blessing you to return safely.

911
00:34:47,860 --> 00:34:48,380
Yes.

912
00:34:48,380 --> 00:34:50,310
Paying my respects to you, Master.

913
00:34:51,050 --> 00:34:53,300
Who moved my hall scroll?

914
00:34:53,530 --> 00:34:54,330
Uncle, Uncle.

915
00:34:54,420 --> 00:34:56,010
-Who?
-I…

916
00:34:56,010 --> 00:34:56,820
I moved it

917
00:34:56,820 --> 00:34:57,970
aside to clean.

918
00:34:57,970 --> 00:34:59,820
I'll put it back as soon as I'm finished.

919
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:00,940
Who are you?

920
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:03,340
And who is this holding the fish?

921
00:35:03,340 --> 00:35:04,390
Who are they?

922
00:35:05,170 --> 00:35:05,870
Master.

923
00:35:05,970 --> 00:35:08,130
Isn't this your good nephew?

924
00:35:08,220 --> 00:35:11,220
This couple has been looking forward
to your return.

925
00:35:13,340 --> 00:35:14,700
You are Yunqi?

926
00:35:15,220 --> 00:35:16,380
I am Yunqi.

927
00:35:16,490 --> 00:35:17,650
Zhang Yunqi?

928
00:35:17,700 --> 00:35:18,900
Zhang Yunqi.

929
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:21,170
My good nephew?

930
00:35:21,570 --> 00:35:22,450
Uncle.

931
00:35:22,940 --> 00:35:24,740
You finally recognized me.

932
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:27,700
I am your good nephew.

933
00:35:27,780 --> 00:35:28,770
Uncle.

934
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:30,360
Do you remember

935
00:35:30,570 --> 00:35:32,600
when I was little,

936
00:35:32,650 --> 00:35:34,450
I even pooped on

937
00:35:34,450 --> 00:35:37,050
your arm?

938
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:39,490
That's right.

939
00:35:39,610 --> 00:35:40,820
That's right.

940
00:35:41,020 --> 00:35:42,140
That's right.

941
00:35:42,970 --> 00:35:44,760
Master, have you forgotten?

942
00:35:44,820 --> 00:35:46,640
I told you on the way.

943
00:35:46,740 --> 00:35:47,610
Didn't I tell you

944
00:35:47,610 --> 00:35:50,410
housing in the concession
is very tight right now,

945
00:35:50,450 --> 00:35:52,420
so your good nephew

946
00:35:52,420 --> 00:35:53,300
helped you

947
00:35:53,450 --> 00:35:55,530
rent out all these rooms?

948
00:35:55,780 --> 00:35:57,570
It's not what he said.

949
00:35:57,740 --> 00:35:59,130
Not what?

950
00:35:59,170 --> 00:36:01,130
Now that Master is back.

951
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:02,010
Firstly,

952
00:36:02,300 --> 00:36:03,130
your good nephew

953
00:36:03,130 --> 00:36:05,570
will definitely vacate the best room

954
00:36:05,740 --> 00:36:07,090
for you immediately.

955
00:36:07,230 --> 00:36:08,100
Right, nephew?

956
00:36:08,700 --> 00:36:10,350
Yes, Uncle.

957
00:36:11,170 --> 00:36:11,780
Secondly,

958
00:36:12,010 --> 00:36:13,490
your dear nephew

959
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:14,300
has collected

960
00:36:14,300 --> 00:36:15,740
all the rent for you.

961
00:36:15,860 --> 00:36:17,820
He'll be bringing it over shortly.

962
00:36:18,260 --> 00:36:19,300
Right, nephew?

963
00:36:23,130 --> 00:36:24,340
That's right?

964
00:36:24,340 --> 00:36:25,650
That's right, Uncle.

965
00:36:27,610 --> 00:36:28,860
The clouds have cleared—

966
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:30,260
everyone's happy now.

967
00:36:30,340 --> 00:36:30,940
Master. Master.

968
00:36:30,940 --> 00:36:32,170
Eat. Eat.

969
00:36:37,610 --> 00:36:39,090
All that shouting and fuss,

970
00:36:39,090 --> 00:36:40,700
just for a piece of fish?

971
00:36:41,250 --> 00:36:42,080
Master,

972
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:43,420
I think

973
00:36:43,450 --> 00:36:44,340
in this whole house,

974
00:36:44,340 --> 00:36:45,010
only you

975
00:36:45,040 --> 00:36:47,770
deserve this fish.

976
00:36:47,790 --> 00:36:48,500
Because

977
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:50,130
you are the rightful

978
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:52,720
landlord of this house.

979
00:36:52,750 --> 00:36:54,350
That's right.

980
00:36:54,370 --> 00:36:54,940
Right,

981
00:36:54,970 --> 00:36:55,900
nephew's wife?

982
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,170
Of course.

983
00:36:57,940 --> 00:36:58,740
Right, nephew?

984
00:36:58,740 --> 00:37:00,340
Get lost. Who's your nephew?

985
00:37:00,570 --> 00:37:01,570
Nephew.

986
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:02,590
Uncle.

987
00:37:03,130 --> 00:37:05,300
The fish will taste fishy if it gets cold.

988
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:06,700
I'll go heat it up for you.

989
00:37:07,700 --> 00:37:09,560
I'll heat up the soup for you, too.

990
00:37:09,820 --> 00:37:11,030
I want to eat duck

991
00:37:11,090 --> 00:37:12,300
and chili oil.

992
00:37:12,510 --> 00:37:13,440
We have them all.

993
00:37:18,490 --> 00:37:19,700
Dad. Dad.

994
00:37:20,300 --> 00:37:21,490
Go upstairs.

995
00:37:21,490 --> 00:37:22,890
I'll show you something.

996
00:37:23,300 --> 00:37:25,090
I need to tell you something.

997
00:37:25,090 --> 00:37:25,940
Right, Master.

998
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:26,870
Hurry upstairs.

999
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:27,860
-Okay.
-Go upstairs.

1000
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:28,530
Okay. Okay. Okay.

1001
00:37:28,530 --> 00:37:29,170
Okay.

1002
00:37:46,570 --> 00:37:48,440
This is Yunkui's child?

1003
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:50,420
It's your grandson, Dad.

1004
00:37:54,050 --> 00:37:55,450
I have a grandson.

1005
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:03,940
Have you named the child?

1006
00:38:05,090 --> 00:38:06,780
Yunkui always said

1007
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:09,300
you should be the one to name him.

1008
00:38:10,610 --> 00:38:11,260
Okay.

1009
00:38:11,900 --> 00:38:12,820
I'll name him.

1010
00:38:14,780 --> 00:38:15,620
According to

1011
00:38:15,640 --> 00:38:18,510
the Zhang family genealogy back in Haiwen,

1012
00:38:19,700 --> 00:38:22,420
we follow the sequence:
Wen, Ru, Yun, Yue, Jing.

1013
00:38:22,610 --> 00:38:24,380
Since Yunkui is the "Yun" generation,

1014
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:27,300
his child belongs to the "Yue" generation.

1015
00:38:27,780 --> 00:38:28,780
Let me think.

1016
00:38:29,220 --> 00:38:30,300
Let me think.

1017
00:38:34,820 --> 00:38:38,780
Everyone has their stormy days.

1018
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:43,650
Every cloud has a silver lining—Yueming.

1019
00:38:44,740 --> 00:38:46,700
Shall we call him Yueming?

1020
00:38:47,610 --> 00:38:50,900
Every cloud has a silver...

1021
00:38:52,580 --> 00:38:53,350
Dad.

1022
00:38:54,170 --> 00:38:56,050
Yueming sounds nice.

1023
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:59,230
Yueming.

1024
00:39:03,570 --> 00:39:04,700
Yunkui,

1025
00:39:05,130 --> 00:39:07,420
your son is called Yueming.

1026
00:39:07,820 --> 00:39:09,220
Yueming.

1027
00:39:10,650 --> 00:39:11,700
Zhang Yueming.

1028
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:13,220
It's a good name.

1029
00:39:13,700 --> 00:39:15,150
You have a name now, kid.

1030
00:39:15,260 --> 00:39:17,010
Yueming. Yueming. Yueming.

1031
00:39:20,300 --> 00:39:21,490
Mrs. Liu!

1032
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:23,170
Mrs. Liu!

1033
00:39:23,700 --> 00:39:24,700
Master. Master.

1034
00:39:24,860 --> 00:39:26,380
Why are you calling Mrs. Liu?

1035
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,530
In the second drawer

1036
00:39:27,530 --> 00:39:29,690
of the bookshelf in my study,

1037
00:39:29,780 --> 00:39:33,000
there is a golden lock
and a bracelet prepared for the child.

1038
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,200
Ask her to bring them.

1039
00:39:34,610 --> 00:39:35,420
Mrs. Liu!

1040
00:39:35,420 --> 00:39:36,940
Master, Master.

1041
00:39:36,940 --> 00:39:38,210
Mrs. Liu left.

1042
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:40,170
She went back to the countryside.
Have you forgotten?

1043
00:39:40,170 --> 00:39:41,170
She went back?

1044
00:39:42,300 --> 00:39:44,300
Why didn't she say goodbye to me?

1045
00:39:45,450 --> 00:39:46,610
Well, Master,

1046
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:48,520
she asked your permission,

1047
00:39:48,610 --> 00:39:49,550
and you agreed.

1048
00:39:49,650 --> 00:39:51,370
How could she go back
without your permission?

1049
00:39:51,370 --> 00:39:52,160
Right?

1050
00:39:53,610 --> 00:39:54,740
That's right.

1051
00:39:57,050 --> 00:39:59,490
Why am I getting more and more muddled?

1052
00:40:02,420 --> 00:40:03,150
But Yueming,

1053
00:40:03,170 --> 00:40:04,690
it's okay. It's okay.

1054
00:40:04,780 --> 00:40:05,490
Look,

1055
00:40:05,860 --> 00:40:08,060
Grandpa's still got something for you.

1056
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:08,940
Look.

1057
00:40:10,170 --> 00:40:13,050
This is a gift for you.

1058
00:40:22,050 --> 00:40:24,170
Yueming.

1059
00:40:24,780 --> 00:40:26,380
Yueming.

1060
00:40:30,820 --> 00:40:32,420
What's wrong with my father?

1061
00:40:33,650 --> 00:40:34,740
Good boy.

1062
00:40:50,090 --> 00:40:51,860
What I said downstairs

1063
00:40:52,010 --> 00:40:53,530
was just to fool them.

1064
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:57,250
I found Master in the refugee shelter.

1065
00:40:57,970 --> 00:40:59,380
The refugee shelter?

1066
00:41:00,340 --> 00:41:01,740
When I found him,

1067
00:41:01,910 --> 00:41:03,100
he was unshaven

1068
00:41:03,300 --> 00:41:05,240
and wearing a tattered old coat
someone had given him.

1069
00:41:05,240 --> 00:41:06,880
He was talking nonsense.

1070
00:41:07,260 --> 00:41:09,180
It was clear he had suffered terribly

1071
00:41:09,180 --> 00:41:10,940
and gone through great hardships.

1072
00:41:10,940 --> 00:41:13,380
As soon as I picked him up
from there,

1073
00:41:13,700 --> 00:41:15,100
I took him to see a doctor.

1074
00:41:15,650 --> 00:41:16,510
The doctor said

1075
00:41:16,900 --> 00:41:18,940
he had taken a heavy blow to the head,

1076
00:41:19,050 --> 00:41:20,780
and the shock affected him mentally.

1077
00:41:20,780 --> 00:41:22,050
That's why he's lucid one moment

1078
00:41:22,050 --> 00:41:23,310
and confused the next.

1079
00:41:23,970 --> 00:41:24,940
But don't worry.

1080
00:41:25,380 --> 00:41:26,300
The doctor also said

1081
00:41:26,300 --> 00:41:27,830
that as long as he rests well

1082
00:41:28,010 --> 00:41:29,470
and isn't agitated again,

1083
00:41:29,570 --> 00:41:30,970
he should recover soon.

1084
00:41:32,780 --> 00:41:33,900
Where did his outfit

1085
00:41:33,900 --> 00:41:35,300
come from?

1086
00:41:35,570 --> 00:41:36,570
And this box...

1087
00:41:36,970 --> 00:41:38,500
I've never seen it, either.

1088
00:41:45,960 --> 00:41:46,930
[Collection of Treasures]

1089
00:41:52,700 --> 00:41:53,340
This...

1090
00:41:58,080 --> 00:41:59,610
When I found him,

1091
00:41:59,700 --> 00:42:01,110
his money,

1092
00:42:01,340 --> 00:42:01,970
land deed,

1093
00:42:01,970 --> 00:42:03,170
and rare books

1094
00:42:03,220 --> 00:42:04,090
were all gone.

1095
00:42:04,220 --> 00:42:05,420
I guess he was robbed.

1096
00:42:05,650 --> 00:42:06,510
I thought,

1097
00:42:06,740 --> 00:42:08,610
if he came back like that

1098
00:42:08,740 --> 00:42:10,090
and the couple saw him,

1099
00:42:10,820 --> 00:42:12,610
they would eat you two alive.

1100
00:42:13,450 --> 00:42:15,610
So I used the private savings
Xiaoyue gave me,

1101
00:42:15,610 --> 00:42:17,170
the money from selling

1102
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,920
the ferry tickets to Wuhan,

1103
00:42:19,010 --> 00:42:20,010
and some advance wages

1104
00:42:20,010 --> 00:42:21,260
from my boss

1105
00:42:21,420 --> 00:42:22,860
to get him cleaned up,

1106
00:42:22,860 --> 00:42:23,650
see a doctor,

1107
00:42:23,760 --> 00:42:25,020
and properly dressed.

1108
00:42:25,050 --> 00:42:26,830
We have to come back decently.

1109
00:42:26,900 --> 00:42:30,100
We couldn't let those two bastards
stir up trouble again.

1110
00:42:32,860 --> 00:42:33,820
You take this.

1111
00:42:34,090 --> 00:42:35,450
When he is more clear-headed,

1112
00:42:35,450 --> 00:42:36,250
give it to him.

1113
00:42:38,380 --> 00:42:39,980
How much did you spend?

1114
00:42:40,050 --> 00:42:41,380
W-Write it down.

1115
00:42:41,380 --> 00:42:43,380
I will pay you back when I have money.

1116
00:42:43,740 --> 00:42:45,450
No rush. No rush.

1117
00:42:45,900 --> 00:42:47,230
I'm just reminding you.

1118
00:42:47,340 --> 00:42:48,900
Now that Master is back,

1119
00:42:49,090 --> 00:42:51,540
you should quickly set rules
for those two bastards

1120
00:42:51,540 --> 00:42:52,740
and get the rent back.

1121
00:42:52,970 --> 00:42:54,770
Then I'll also get my money back.

1122
00:42:54,880 --> 00:42:56,680
That's true.

1123
00:42:59,700 --> 00:43:00,610
Well...

1124
00:43:01,220 --> 00:43:03,010
the "That's right"—

1125
00:43:03,130 --> 00:43:04,340
What exactly do you mean by that?
